@startuml
title Admin Monitoring Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Admin Controller" as Ctrl
database "Database" as DB

== View Logs ==
Admin -> FE: View Security Logs
FE -> API: GET /admin/logs
API -> Ctrl: Authorize
Ctrl -> DB: Fetch Security Logs (Paginated)
DB --> Ctrl: Logs
Ctrl --> API: Logs Response

== View Stats ==
Admin -> FE: View Dashboard Stats
FE -> API: GET /admin/stats
API -> Ctrl: Authorize
Ctrl -> DB: Aggregate User/Note Counts
DB --> Ctrl: Statistics
Ctrl --> API: Stats Response

@enduml
